posting_body: ['Looking for a great place to live?', 'Where someone will remember your name.', "It's a quiet building with lovely neighbors.", '\u2028 We have a beautiful apartment available.', '2 bedroom for $1,150 a month!', 'Security Deposit is same as the rent.', '$25 Application fee per adult.', 'We offer-', 'FREE Wi-Fi.', 'Newer Carpet.', 'Newer Appliances.', 'New/Newer Paint.', 'Blinds.', 'Large  windows.', 'Eat-in kitchens.', 'Free storage available.', 'Monthly rent raffle.', 'Heating, water, and trash all PAID!', 'Off street parking available.', '\u2028We also have garages to rent.', 'Large laundry room with newer washers and dryers.', '\u2028We are pet friendly, small dogs and cats welcome!', '$250 Refundable pet deposit.', 'We are non-smoking, but you are welcome to smoke outside.', 'Fantastic resident service and timely maintenance.', 'Also we are 4blks from Lake Phalen, walking paths, and bike trails.', 'Close to great parks and schools.', 'White Bear Ave. stores and restaurants.', '10 mins to Downtown St. Paul.', '\u2028 We are even on the bus line.', '64D to Maplewood or Downtown.', 'We look forward to hearing from you!', 'Call Penny today to set up your appointment!', 'show contact info']
